originalText.text: I can't imagine my life without Kathleen.  As much as her actual training is valuable, she is a great listener and can adjust what I need on the spot.  She is fine with discomfort from all those tough reps, but never with pain.  I have been working with Kathleen for more than five years and find her helpful and a pleasure to work with.

originalText.text: Kathleen is an excellent trainer. She’s super knowledgeable. She always asks the right questions and really listens to how her clients are feeling. I started training with Kathleen after a number of injuries and my body feels better and stronger because of her. She really focuses on form which has made a world of difference. I still have work to do but I’m happy I have Kathleen to help me on this path forward.

originalText.text:
I started working with Kathleen after my PT recommended her. I only see her once a week but I get so much out of our session. Working with her has been a great investment!

Not only does she help me with my strength workouts, but she also helped me with my pelvic issues that started after I gave birth. I have seen improvement in my day to day life and my performance in multi sports. Each session is well spent as I leave with more knowledge in preventing injuries, balancing workouts and recovery and better form.

originalText.text:
I started working with Kathleen just recently and can already say that her method and approach made a huge difference in how I feel. She is big on setting you up with proper form, incorporating breath work while engaging your core so that your body is strengthened and supported in ways you haven’t felt before. I felt my abs “turn on” after the very first session with Kathleen like never before, and have noticed a remarkable difference in how much more engaged my core has become in everyday activities.

I absolutely recommend working with Kathleen. She is a pro when it comes to movement and will get you to become your best and strongest self.

originalText.text: Working with Kathleen has been the best investment I have made. She's helped me progressively build strength, get comfortable in the gym, and work through ACLR surgery and back pain. Her programming is incredible, and thoughtfully crafted to help me achieve my goals. I highly recommend!
